original_title: Yousei Teikoku - 15th Anniversary PAX VESANIA LIVE TOUR
overview: Features a 25-song concert celebrating Yousei Teikoku's 15th anniversary. Takarano Arika of "ALI PROJECT" makes a guest appearance in two songs. The performance was held at STUDIO COAST on June 16, 2013.
title: Yousei Teikoku - 15th Anniversary PAX VESANIA LIVE TOUR
